4334a3112ca77a","tid":529820,"uid":53498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-15T14:22:01.000Z","msg":"明明自己失平衡"},{"pid":"0bc84ae671a44da752e2189c835e0e53d5d95e0b","tid":529820,"uid":53498,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"8ba10b93ce40d0b64a6dd77d9e0d3b0fd68c4b06","tid":529820,"uid":57035,"like":79,"dislike":1,"score":78,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-15T08:00:13.000Z","msg":"你當秦沛流架?<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.eurosport.com/2010/09/22/643583-21865876-2560-1440.jpg?w=700\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.eurosport.com%2F2010%2F09%2F22%2F643583-21865876-2560-1440.jpg%3Fw%3D700&h=111232e4&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-15T14:23:18.000Z","msg":"呢條撚樣近廿幾年都無得輸,爭在韓狗未立士巴拿打人"},{"pid":"c4af9426995443e31e2956d150ceb82a82ff1faa","tid":529820,"uid":50055,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-15T14:25:57.000Z","msg":"踢人球證被無限期停賽<br />\n<br />\n【<a href=\"http://now.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnow.com&d=H04InM%2BlYy8Za4FUzunqCm6tz0R9Svbxs0EcWe5CwMI%3D&h=d1771ac6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">now.com</a>體育】法國足總在周一宣佈，處罰於周日法甲踢人的球證查邦停賽，而且將會就事件進行紀律聆訊。<br />\n<br />\n「查邦（Tony Chapron）本來會在周三昂熱對特魯瓦的法甲執法，現在已被抽起，他很快就會跟法國足總紀律委員會會面。」法國足總在聲明中未有表示查邦何時會復出。<br />\n<br />\n法國足總續指，查邦在重看過比賽片段後，認為自己跌倒是意外，因此已準備了報告交予紀律委員會。法國電台RMC更指，45歲的他將會要求取消向南特後衛迪亞高卡路士出示的第2面黃牌。<br />\n<br />\n在周日舉行的法甲，巴黎聖日耳門作客以1:0小勝南特。於下半場補時階段，查邦被迪亞高卡路士撞跌，之後竟然踢對方報復，更向這名24歲巴西守將出示第2面黃牌，驅逐他離場。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://sports.now.com/home/news/details?id=20057478901\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fsports.now.com%2Fhome%2Fnews%2Fdetails%3Fid%3D20057478901&d=H04InM%2BlYy8Za4FUzunqCm6tz0R9Svbxs0EcWe5CwMI%3D&h=d3a5edff\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://sports.now.com/home/news/details?id=20057478901</a>"},{"pid":"ba81efbe93ac2012851ec677e9bf047fd65ed35f","tid":529820,"uid":143620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-15T14:28:28.000Z","msg":"咁個球員下場係咪要停賽"}]}